Company Overview of Saxon Woods Advisors LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Saxon Woods Advisors, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, typically high net worth individuals. It also manages accounts for pension and profit sharing plans, family foundations, endowments, and charitable organizations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income of the United States. The firm also manages mutual funds for its clients. It operates as a subsidiary of Alpine Woods Investments LLC. Saxon Woods Advisors was founded in 1999 and is based in Purchase, New York.


2500 Westchester AvenueSuite 215Purchase, NY 10577United StatesFounded in 1999



Phone: 914-251-0880

Fax: 914-251-9098








